name: .KINE File Extension
summary: Learn about .KINE files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: You can open a KINE file in version 5 and above of KineMaster (Android, iOS). To do so, you must first create a new project, and then click the Import Project button. Then, navigate to and import your KINE file.
